{"serial": "52065", "department_serial": 51, "code": "CEA058", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Advanced Operating Systems", "ch": "高等作業系統"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen Tseng-Yi"], "ch": ["陳增益"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["A", "B", "C"]}, "loc": {"building": "E6", "room": "A203"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 40, "department": {"ch": "資訊工程學系", "en": "Department of Computer Science and Elec. Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士在職專班", "en": "Master Programme (Adult Learning)"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 9, "selected": 13, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "高等作業系統課程的目標在於深入理解作業系統的高級概念、設計和實現。這包括瞭解作業系統的結構、管理資源的方法、以及如何處理硬件和軟件的互動。學生將學習如何設計和實現作業系統的各個組件，包括進程管理、記憶體管理、檔案系統和輸入輸出系統。此外，課程可能還會探討作業系統的安全性、網絡功能和分佈式系統的集成。", "en": "The objectives of an Advanced Operating Systems course are to deeply understand the advanced concepts, design, and implementation of operating systems. This includes comprehending the structure of operating systems, methods of managing resources, and how to handle interactions between hardware and software. Students will learn how to design and implement various components of an operating system, including process management, memory management, file systems, and input/output systems. Additionally, the course may also cover aspects of operating system security, networking capabilities, and integration of distributed systems."}, "outline": {"ch": "高等作業系統的課程涵蓋以下幾個模組：\n1.程序管理\n•程序和執行序的概念與區別\n•程序生命週期、調度算法和程序通信\n2.記憶體管理\n•記憶體分配和回收\n•虛擬記憶體、分頁和分段\n3.檔案系統與儲存管理\n•檔案系統的結構和實現\n•磁碟管理和排程\n4.作業系統安全性\n•系統安全威脅和保護機制\n•使用者身份驗證、存取控制和加密技術\n5.當代與未來的作業系統\n•探討新興的作業系統技術和趨勢\n•雲計算、物聯網和人工智能在作業系統中的應用", "en": "The Advanced Operating Systems course covers the following modules:\n1.Process Management\n•Concepts and distinctions between processes and threads\n•Process lifecycle, scheduling algorithms, and inter-process communication\n2.Memory Management\n•Allocation and deallocation of memory\n•Virtual memory, paging, and segmentation\n3.File Systems and Storage Management\n•Structure and implementation of file systems\n•Disk management and scheduling\n4.Operating System Security\n•System security threats and protection mechanisms\n•User authentication, access control, and encryption techniques\n5.Contemporary and Future Operating Systems\n•Exploration of emerging operating system technologies and trends\n•Applications of cloud computing, the Internet of Things (IoT), and artificial intelligence in operating systems"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Operating Systems: Three Easy Pieces", "en": "Operating Systems: Three Easy Pieces"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "10", "en": "10"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.作業 20％\n2.期中報告 25％\n3.期未考試 30％\n4.期末專題 25％", "en": "1.Assignment 20％\n2.Midterm report 25％\n3.Final exam 30％\n4.Final project 25％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "按事先預約的時間", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "期末專題實作以及報告", "en": "Final project demonstration"}, "domain": {"ch": "資安、網路、資料庫與系統研究群", "en": "資安、網路、資料庫與系統研究群"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "資訊工程專業知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用與解決問題之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "組織表達能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "創新及獨立思考之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "溝通協調與團隊合作能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "瞭解資訊潮流與國際趨勢", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及社會責任", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["無"]}, {"competencies": "終身學習與自我成長之能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Domain Knowled